WEBVTT

01:27.400 --> 01:31.900
[The Dark Romance]

01:32.200 --> 01:34.950
[Episode 3]

01:35.020 --> 01:37.220
[Outpatient]

01:37.220 --> 01:38.289
[Lihai Renxin Hospital]

01:50.400 --> 01:52.560
I'll prescribe a week's worth
of medication for you.

01:52.560 --> 01:53.690
It's not addictive,

01:53.870 --> 01:55.270
so take it without worry.

01:59.700 --> 02:00.300
It's fine.

02:02.200 --> 02:03.640
You're my psychiatrist.

02:04.070 --> 02:07.270
What gives you the right
to send me to another department?

02:07.760 --> 02:08.560
Li Changning.

02:09.680 --> 02:11.210
You're disrupting my work.

02:11.280 --> 02:12.680
Why did you send me...

02:14.520 --> 02:16.050
to that kind of department?

02:17.520 --> 02:19.329
Because I believe you donated eggs,

02:19.329 --> 02:20.450
being completely irresponsible

02:20.450 --> 02:22.380
with your body, just to make money.

02:23.190 --> 02:24.280
Those marks on your stomach

02:24.280 --> 02:25.870
were from
ovulation stimulation injections.

02:25.870 --> 02:26.630
Be gentle.

02:29.960 --> 02:31.890
And not just once in a short period.

02:32.910 --> 02:35.190
I arranged gynecological examinations
and consultations for you

02:35.190 --> 02:36.190
to help determine

02:37.190 --> 02:38.520
whether you'll ever be able

02:38.520 --> 02:40.450
to have children in your lifetime.

02:42.590 --> 02:44.000
Breaking up isn't the end of the world.

02:44.000 --> 02:47.780
[Smile Service, Warm as Always]

02:44.520 --> 02:45.380
Let me tell you,

02:45.670 --> 02:48.000
a proper ex should be like
he's dead to you.

02:49.079 --> 02:50.710
It's okay to cry on the first day,

02:50.710 --> 02:52.800
but by the second day,
you should delete and block him.

02:52.800 --> 02:55.280
By the third day,
eat what you want, have fun,

02:56.079 --> 02:58.250
and meet a new boyfriend.

03:19.680 --> 03:21.610
You told me to find a new boyfriend.

03:25.079 --> 03:26.680
You can ignore that part.

03:27.400 --> 03:28.280
Sometimes,

03:29.030 --> 03:31.030
being alone is actually quite nice.

03:31.400 --> 03:33.680
As long as one is healthy and happy.

03:35.480 --> 03:36.829
But don't they say

03:37.710 --> 03:39.170
lovers will stay together

03:39.840 --> 03:40.840
forever?

03:54.960 --> 03:56.030
It's my fault.

03:56.470 --> 03:57.710
It's my bad.

03:58.910 --> 04:01.540
I lost the love lock necklace he gave me.

04:01.680 --> 04:04.080
He said I didn't cherish our relationship.

04:04.620 --> 04:05.340
But I did.

04:06.910 --> 04:07.800
I really did.

04:07.900 --> 04:10.760
The one who didn't cherish it
certainly wasn't you.

04:10.870 --> 04:13.400
He must have known
your financial situation.

04:13.400 --> 04:14.470
You bought him a phone

04:14.470 --> 04:15.750
and rented an apartment.

04:15.750 --> 04:16.870
Didn't he ever ask you

04:16.870 --> 04:18.329
where the money came from?

04:20.510 --> 04:21.709
After egg retrieval,

04:22.040 --> 04:24.170
one can't have sex for at least 14 days.

04:24.360 --> 04:26.720
Your frequent, unregulated egg donations

04:26.720 --> 04:29.320
have severely damaged
your ovarian function.

04:30.120 --> 04:30.950
And

04:32.510 --> 04:35.440
you had
completely unprotected sexual activities.

04:36.830 --> 04:38.360
Your infection is so severe

04:38.380 --> 04:39.770
that I find it hard to believe

04:39.770 --> 04:40.850
he didn't notice.

04:42.790 --> 04:44.390
Did he really care about you,

04:45.270 --> 04:46.070
Li Changning?

04:50.870 --> 04:51.930
So in the future...

04:53.510 --> 04:54.440
So in the future,

04:56.360 --> 04:58.290
will I not be able to have children?

04:59.070 --> 05:00.200
That depends on you.

05:01.670 --> 05:04.270
If you follow the doctor's treatment
properly

05:04.350 --> 05:06.480
and don't abuse yourself like before,

05:07.150 --> 05:07.940
I believe

05:08.720 --> 05:10.980
you'll still have a chance to be a mother.

05:21.800 --> 05:22.600
You hear that?

05:23.240 --> 05:24.700
What kind of sound is that?

05:33.070 --> 05:34.530
Its foot is injured.

05:36.040 --> 05:36.430
Yes.

05:37.510 --> 05:38.909
Bitten by its boyfriend.

05:40.680 --> 05:41.810
How did this happen?

05:42.270 --> 05:44.190
Fortunately,
the store clerk found it in time;

05:44.190 --> 05:46.240
otherwise,
it would've been bitten to death.

05:46.240 --> 05:48.500
Hamsters are very territorial animals.

05:49.000 --> 05:50.720
Mothers, their offspring,

05:51.070 --> 05:53.190
or even male and female hamsters
after mating

05:53.190 --> 05:54.920
will all fight with each other.

06:01.330 --> 06:02.660
Your boyfriend bit you.

06:03.480 --> 06:04.610
You must be very sad.

06:05.720 --> 06:07.180
But it's also very strong.

06:08.920 --> 06:10.720
It quickly came to terms with it.

06:11.240 --> 06:13.030
Not only did it stop feeling sad,

06:13.030 --> 06:14.310
but it bit back hard.

06:15.400 --> 06:16.930
It saved itself from death.

06:22.630 --> 06:23.620
I bought it home.

06:23.920 --> 06:25.310
But I've been busy lately.

06:25.310 --> 06:27.590
I'm afraid I won't have time
to take good care of it.

06:27.590 --> 06:28.630
Could I trouble you

06:28.630 --> 06:30.290
to look after it for a few days?

06:33.690 --> 06:35.290
By the time its wounds heal,

06:35.430 --> 06:37.760
you should be ready
to leave the hospital.

06:49.220 --> 06:52.350
[Police]

07:32.050 --> 07:34.810
This little horse
was Godmother's favorite.

07:35.480 --> 07:37.600
She said Godfather gave it to her.

07:38.540 --> 07:39.490
Now that Godmother is gone,

07:39.490 --> 07:42.420
Godfather must be even more heartbroken
than we are.

07:46.720 --> 07:47.780
So we'll keep it...

07:49.350 --> 07:50.480
for Godmother.

08:17.060 --> 08:17.460
[Cangshan District, Lihai City,
Dongchuan Province]

08:17.480 --> 08:17.950
[920 Xiangan Road]
[To Jian Leilei]

08:25.650 --> 08:27.780
[Demand Letter]

08:30.390 --> 08:36.380
[Demand Letter] [Zirui Finance]

08:39.770 --> 08:47.060
[Demand Letter]

08:40.039 --> 08:42.570
No wonder
she misappropriated client funds.

08:43.150 --> 08:44.810
She even mortgaged her house.

08:45.470 --> 08:47.790
If the repayment is not completed
within 30 days,

08:47.790 --> 08:49.850
the house will be seized for auction.

08:52.270 --> 08:54.470
This house meant everything to Leilei.

08:54.880 --> 08:56.740
The day she paid off her mortgage,

08:57.020 --> 08:59.410
she even treated Jiale and me to dinner.

09:00.450 --> 09:02.050
How could she bear to lose it?

09:02.960 --> 09:05.080
Did she trade crypto with leverage?

09:05.510 --> 09:06.840
Because with leverage,

09:07.030 --> 09:08.290
once there are losses,

09:08.390 --> 09:10.520
she must meet the margin requirement.

09:10.870 --> 09:11.540
Otherwise,

09:12.000 --> 09:13.200
they'll force her
to liquidate her position,

09:13.200 --> 09:14.150
and she'll lose everything.

09:14.150 --> 09:16.550
In that case, she might mortgage anything.

09:16.550 --> 09:18.210
Do you think this loan company

09:18.790 --> 09:20.120
might be connected with

09:20.120 --> 09:22.600
the platform
where Leilei lost her investment?

09:22.600 --> 09:24.600
But didn't you check
her investment company?

09:24.600 --> 09:25.750
You said it was legitimate.

09:25.750 --> 09:27.680
Look into this loan company again.

09:32.360 --> 09:33.360
Are you and Jiale

09:34.450 --> 09:35.300
okay now?

09:36.840 --> 09:37.500
We're fine.

09:38.400 --> 09:39.470
Thanks to Dr. Luo.

09:40.480 --> 09:41.120
Dr. Luo?

09:41.550 --> 09:42.600
W-What?

09:42.600 --> 09:43.330
What Dr. Luo?

09:43.440 --> 09:44.500
You don't know him.

09:44.600 --> 09:45.800
He's a psychologist.

09:52.840 --> 09:54.970
You're just using this to look into it?

09:55.200 --> 09:56.360
I've already checked all this.

09:56.360 --> 09:58.290
I came to you because I had no leads.

09:58.480 --> 10:00.940
I thought you had
some special connections.

10:02.080 --> 10:04.340
I-I'm just an ordinary person.

10:04.820 --> 10:07.420
It's easy for me
to check the weather forecast.

10:08.870 --> 10:10.400
Alright then, I'm leaving.

10:10.870 --> 10:11.870
Aren't you going home yet?

10:11.870 --> 10:13.600
I-I'm working overtime today.

10:13.960 --> 10:14.670
I'm sorry

10:14.670 --> 10:15.390
for bothering you.

10:15.390 --> 10:16.190
No, not at all.

10:16.390 --> 10:16.670
Oh, right.

10:16.670 --> 10:17.240
Um,

10:17.550 --> 10:18.620
about the money,

10:19.320 --> 10:21.050
if it really needs to be repaid,

10:21.240 --> 10:22.120
I can still provide it.

10:22.120 --> 10:23.030
No, no need.

10:23.110 --> 10:24.640
It's not your place anyway.

10:25.080 --> 10:26.540
I'll think of another way.

10:27.670 --> 10:28.360
I'm leaving now.

10:28.360 --> 10:29.150
Okay, okay.

10:30.510 --> 10:31.710
Don't worry too much.

10:57.880 --> 10:59.550
We found a trunk full of luxury goods

10:59.550 --> 11:01.440
in Jian Leilei's car trunk.

11:01.550 --> 11:03.080
They're roughly estimated

11:03.120 --> 11:04.850
to be worth nearly one million.

11:04.870 --> 11:07.080
Only her fingerprints were on the box.

11:10.900 --> 11:12.080
I'm sorry, Ma'am.

11:12.140 --> 11:14.690
Our store can't accept these items.

11:18.080 --> 11:19.000
Why?

11:20.080 --> 11:22.600
We can't verify their authenticity.

11:24.030 --> 11:25.830
I have receipts for all of these.

11:26.790 --> 11:29.200
Counterfeiting is rampant
in the luxury market now.

11:29.200 --> 11:29.960
Many fake products

11:29.960 --> 11:31.390
can be indistinguishable
from the real ones.

11:31.390 --> 11:32.360
They even have

11:32.360 --> 11:34.240
complete packages including invoices,

11:34.240 --> 11:35.750
full packaging,

11:35.750 --> 11:36.870
and even credit card receipts.

11:36.870 --> 11:38.400
These most valuable items—

11:38.510 --> 11:39.200
these bags,

11:39.670 --> 11:41.670
this diamond watch, and this bracelet—

11:41.670 --> 11:43.960
are all counterfeits
after our verification.

11:43.960 --> 11:44.910
Counterfeits?

11:46.630 --> 11:48.480
Only official boutique purchases
are authentic-guaranteed.

11:48.480 --> 11:50.880
Other channels, like personal shoppers,

11:50.960 --> 11:52.030
might sell fakes.

11:55.000 --> 11:56.660
What about this little horse?

12:08.600 --> 12:09.090
Xia Yi.

12:09.120 --> 12:09.790
Sorry.

12:10.240 --> 12:13.370
The number you have dialed
is temporarily unavailable.

12:13.550 --> 12:15.140
Please try again later.

12:18.630 --> 12:19.530
It's also fake.

12:23.930 --> 12:26.070
[Premium Pawnshop]

12:29.120 --> 12:32.250
The number you have dialed
is temporarily unavailable.

12:32.320 --> 12:33.860
Please try again later.

12:33.790 --> 12:35.320
[Police Reminder] [No Fighting]
[Losers in Hospital; Winners in Jail]

12:39.160 --> 12:39.920
Officer Li.

12:41.750 --> 12:42.320
Ms. Yan.

12:45.030 --> 12:45.690
What is it?

12:46.350 --> 12:48.820
[Police]

12:46.630 --> 12:48.670
Xia Yi said he was with you that day.

12:49.140 --> 12:50.240
He said you had a good chat.

12:50.240 --> 12:51.120
Is that right?

12:51.480 --> 12:51.910
Yes.

12:52.770 --> 12:54.670
He had just returned
from a rescue mission.

12:54.670 --> 12:56.320
After seeing you, he went to the hospital

12:56.320 --> 12:57.530
to visit Leilei's parents.

12:57.530 --> 12:58.720
Seeing who? Me?

12:59.390 --> 13:00.600
We never met.

13:03.130 --> 13:03.550
Well.

13:05.200 --> 13:06.360
He called and said

13:06.360 --> 13:08.080
he received our voicemail

13:08.080 --> 13:09.150
and asked what it was about.

13:09.150 --> 13:11.010
I explained the situation to him.

13:11.240 --> 13:13.080
He knew Jian Leilei's mother
was in the hospital,

13:13.080 --> 13:14.270
so he said he'd find you first

13:14.270 --> 13:15.790
and asked if he could give his statement
after returning.

13:15.790 --> 13:16.920
I said that was fine.

13:17.200 --> 13:18.860
But what did he say after that?

13:19.390 --> 13:20.200
Went...

13:20.200 --> 13:20.720
Went where?

13:20.720 --> 13:21.320
Minzhou.

13:21.440 --> 13:23.030
He said there was a fishing boat accident
in Minzhou.

13:23.030 --> 13:24.630
His rescue team
needed to go provide support.

13:24.630 --> 13:26.360
So I told him to handle his business first

13:26.360 --> 13:27.200
and deal with this when he gets back.

13:27.200 --> 13:28.730
This matter wasn't urgent.

13:29.670 --> 13:31.270
You didn't even see him in person,

13:31.270 --> 13:32.400
and you just agreed?

13:33.790 --> 13:34.840
How can you be a police officer?

13:34.840 --> 13:36.640
What kind of police work is this?

13:37.080 --> 13:39.140
You completely neglected your duty!

13:39.440 --> 13:39.840
Wait.

13:41.440 --> 13:41.960
Ms. Yan.

13:43.030 --> 13:44.840
We rely on evidence in our investigations.

13:44.840 --> 13:45.320
Right?

13:45.790 --> 13:47.270
Jian Leilei committed suicide
out of guilt.

13:47.270 --> 13:48.030
The evidence is complete,

13:48.030 --> 13:48.840
and the chain is clear.

13:48.840 --> 13:50.030
As far as this case is concerned,

13:50.030 --> 13:51.760
there's no problem closing it.

13:52.030 --> 13:53.600
Her financial transactions with Xia Yi

13:53.600 --> 13:55.030
show nothing suspicious.

13:55.030 --> 13:56.490
I've checked everything.

13:56.790 --> 13:58.250
They're not even married.

13:58.610 --> 14:00.790
I asked him to come just to cooperate
with our investigation

14:00.790 --> 14:01.990
and give a statement.

14:02.360 --> 14:03.980
He's not a criminal suspect. I...

14:03.980 --> 14:05.460
Then why did Xia Yi lie to me

14:05.790 --> 14:06.990
about having met you?

14:08.270 --> 14:09.960
He lied about this.

14:10.240 --> 14:10.960
How can you be sure

14:10.960 --> 14:12.890
he hasn't lied about other things?

14:13.050 --> 14:14.510
His phone is unreachable.

14:14.600 --> 14:16.030
The gifts he gave to Leilei are fake.

14:16.030 --> 14:17.090
His car was rented.

14:17.150 --> 14:19.200
We don't even have a single photo of him.

14:19.200 --> 14:20.360
Isn't that strange?

14:20.360 --> 14:22.000
I'll investigate anything suspicious,

14:22.000 --> 14:22.480
okay?

14:23.550 --> 14:25.550
I understand how you feel right now.

14:25.870 --> 14:27.440
But you can't let your emotions

14:27.440 --> 14:28.360
lead you to criticize our law enforcement—

14:28.360 --> 14:29.960
I'm not criticizing law enforcement.

14:29.960 --> 14:31.160
I'm criticizing you.

14:33.190 --> 14:33.930
Uncle.

14:34.410 --> 14:36.030
Did Leilei ever mention

14:36.030 --> 14:37.830
what Xia Yi's company is called?

14:39.930 --> 14:40.660
No.

14:41.600 --> 14:44.240
I heard Xia Yi often sent you
health supplements.

14:44.240 --> 14:46.520
Do you still have any of the packaging

14:46.600 --> 14:47.790
or delivery tracking numbers

14:47.790 --> 14:48.840
from those packages?

14:48.840 --> 14:50.300
They were all bought by Xia

14:50.630 --> 14:52.290
and sent to us through Leilei.

14:52.710 --> 14:55.010
When Xia Yi and Leilei
visited your hometown,

14:55.010 --> 14:56.870
did you take any photos together?

14:57.600 --> 14:59.660
What's wrong? Did something happen?

15:01.870 --> 15:03.200
Nothing. It's nothing.

15:04.340 --> 15:06.390
I just want to gather everything

15:06.410 --> 15:07.470
related to Leilei.

15:08.080 --> 15:09.450
As a keepsake, you know.

15:09.960 --> 15:11.270
Thank you for your thoughtfulness.

15:11.270 --> 15:13.530
But we didn't get a chance to take photos.

15:13.560 --> 15:15.180
They came on the weekend

15:15.440 --> 15:16.930
in such a rush,

15:17.030 --> 15:19.030
and stayed for just one day and left.

15:19.740 --> 15:21.710
Okay, that's all, Uncle.

15:21.840 --> 15:22.770
I'll hang up now.

15:30.580 --> 15:32.860
[Personnel Pool]
[Basic Personnel Information]

15:33.270 --> 15:34.670
Xia Yi.

15:35.970 --> 15:39.590
[Personnel Pool]
[Basic Personnel Information]

15:37.270 --> 15:38.960
Two women, one old man,

15:38.960 --> 15:40.080
and one in prison.

15:40.080 --> 15:41.590
That's all.

15:42.080 --> 15:43.840
Fatty, is Chief Hu's speech ready yet?

15:42.160 --> 15:44.750
[China Police]

15:43.840 --> 15:44.870
Hurry up. He's asking for it.

15:44.870 --> 15:45.970
Working on it, working on it.

15:45.010 --> 15:46.510
[China Police]

15:49.760 --> 15:51.660
Jerk.

15:50.030 --> 15:51.680
[Personnel Pool]
[Basic Personnel Information]

15:52.030 --> 15:53.890
He even dared to lie to the police.

15:54.930 --> 15:55.610
Chief Hu.

16:01.670 --> 16:02.950
What are you doing?

16:05.960 --> 16:07.600
Who told you to investigate this?

16:07.600 --> 16:08.600
Stop it right now.

16:08.960 --> 16:10.490
Explain yourself clearly.

16:12.630 --> 16:13.090
Master.

16:13.840 --> 16:14.900
This is important.

16:15.240 --> 16:16.440
I strongly suspect

16:16.840 --> 16:17.830
that Xia Yi

16:17.910 --> 16:19.110
used a fake identity.

16:20.080 --> 16:21.670
I just checked our system,

16:22.120 --> 16:23.630
and nothing matches up.

16:23.960 --> 16:24.510
And also,

16:24.720 --> 16:26.980
he bought his phone number from a dealer.

16:27.120 --> 16:28.150
He used it for half a year

16:28.150 --> 16:30.410
to almost exclusively call Jian Leilei.

16:30.720 --> 16:32.240
The ID card he used to rent the car

16:32.240 --> 16:33.030
wasn't even his own.

16:33.030 --> 16:34.120
He used an employee's.

16:34.120 --> 16:34.550
Don't you think

16:34.550 --> 16:35.790
we should investigate him

16:35.790 --> 16:37.720
since he was extremely deliberate

16:38.080 --> 16:39.600
about hiding his true information?

16:39.600 --> 16:41.800
What do you say, Master? What do you say?

16:44.550 --> 16:46.670
I've searched the Business Database.

16:46.670 --> 16:49.530
There's no company
associated with the name Xia Yi.

16:49.840 --> 16:51.150
And on the blacklist of dishonest persons,

16:51.150 --> 16:53.010
this name doesn't appear either.

16:55.270 --> 16:56.610
I've checked again

16:57.030 --> 16:59.290
through all my chat history with Leilei.

16:59.870 --> 17:01.930
She never sent me any photos of Xia Yi.

17:03.250 --> 17:04.780
I couldn't reach his phone.

17:05.160 --> 17:07.020
I don't have a single photo of him.

17:07.510 --> 17:09.839
Isn't this like he vanished into thin air?

17:10.589 --> 17:12.460
Maybe we're overthinking this.

17:13.160 --> 17:14.750
If there really is something wrong,

17:14.750 --> 17:16.550
the police wouldn't just
sit around doing nothing.

17:16.550 --> 17:17.920
Don't mention the police to me.

17:17.920 --> 17:20.140
I met a kid who barely has facial hair.

17:20.160 --> 17:21.690
He knew absolutely nothing

17:21.720 --> 17:24.579
and still talked to me
with that bureaucratic tone.

17:26.630 --> 17:27.660
Yan Jiale.

17:28.750 --> 17:30.600
You've come out 5 times already.

17:30.920 --> 17:32.380
What do you want this time?

17:32.430 --> 17:34.160
You already have a girlfriend.

17:34.310 --> 17:36.240
Why are you still here to see my mom?

17:37.350 --> 17:39.350
What nonsense are you talking about?

17:39.350 --> 17:41.510
Your father and I are discussing
important matters.

17:41.510 --> 17:42.910
What important matters?

17:43.310 --> 17:44.310
By the way, Jiale,

17:45.400 --> 17:47.860
when you used to go out
with your godparents,

17:48.370 --> 17:50.230
what kinds of things would you do?

17:50.680 --> 17:51.350
Well,

17:51.350 --> 17:53.410
movies, meals, things like that.

17:53.920 --> 17:55.980
Besides eating and watching movies,

17:56.480 --> 17:57.740
what else would you do?

17:58.160 --> 18:00.360
Last time we went to the hot springs...

18:00.640 --> 18:01.770
Godfather went too.

18:02.270 --> 18:03.920
He's really professional at swimming.

18:03.920 --> 18:06.720
He has a very long scar here.

18:07.070 --> 18:09.190
He said he got cut
by a sunken ship's anchor

18:09.190 --> 18:10.720
during a rescue operation.

18:11.240 --> 18:12.970
Did you take any photos of them?

18:13.030 --> 18:14.560
You never bought me a phone,

18:14.750 --> 18:16.210
so how could I take photos?

18:17.030 --> 18:18.110
What an excuse.

18:18.720 --> 18:19.680
What else?

18:20.640 --> 18:22.640
Godfather is really good at gaming.

18:22.680 --> 18:25.240
He even helped me rank up before.

18:25.680 --> 18:26.550
Gaming?

18:27.370 --> 18:28.080
This is it.

18:28.280 --> 18:29.100
[Fly Fashion Is Here] [Start Now]

18:29.130 --> 18:29.540
[Start]

18:30.110 --> 18:31.640
You have this skin already?

18:32.680 --> 18:33.910
[Social] [Team]

18:33.930 --> 18:34.570
[Friends]

18:37.110 --> 18:37.910
What's wrong?

18:39.830 --> 18:41.420
Godfather deleted his account.

18:40.600 --> 18:42.790
[User Deleted]

18:42.240 --> 18:43.200
Most people who stop playing

18:43.200 --> 18:45.600
would just leave their accounts inactive.

18:45.640 --> 18:48.170
Nobody would actually
delete their account.

18:50.510 --> 18:52.940
[Dongchuan Public Security Bureau]

18:56.000 --> 18:58.580
[Model Collective
for Homicide Case Detection]

19:07.470 --> 19:09.240
[Technical Department]

19:15.390 --> 19:19.200
[Confidentiality System]

19:16.750 --> 19:17.210
Ms. Sun.

19:17.250 --> 19:19.340
I heard you like these little things,

19:19.510 --> 19:20.710
so I brought you one.

19:22.050 --> 19:24.400
I-I also brought you some snacks, Ms. Sun.

19:24.560 --> 19:25.820
Well, these things I brought

19:25.820 --> 19:27.980
are all delicious,
but won't make you gain weight.

19:27.980 --> 19:29.450
They'll leave you speechless, Ms. Sun.

19:28.040 --> 19:32.620
[Confidentiality System]

19:29.470 --> 19:31.000
-Don't give me that.
-Have a taste.

19:31.000 --> 19:32.680
I'm old enough to be your mother.

19:32.680 --> 19:33.740
So disrespectful.

19:34.560 --> 19:35.840
You're just joking.

19:36.640 --> 19:38.030
You're so young.

19:38.960 --> 19:39.510
How could you be my mother?

19:39.510 --> 19:40.880
Even calling you "Ms."
makes you sound too old.

19:40.880 --> 19:41.380
See?

19:42.000 --> 19:43.730
Try it. It's really delicious.

19:44.030 --> 19:44.550
Ms. Sun.

19:51.960 --> 19:53.690
Case filing first for a sketch.

19:56.240 --> 19:56.950
Ms. Sun,

19:57.440 --> 19:59.500
can you do me this small favor?

19:59.790 --> 20:00.160
Just

20:00.510 --> 20:01.200
draw it first.

20:01.200 --> 20:02.330
Besides, even if...

20:02.590 --> 20:03.820
I mean, even if

20:04.070 --> 20:05.120
I do you this favor

20:05.590 --> 20:06.790
and draw this sketch,

20:07.110 --> 20:08.960
you'd still need your eyewitness

20:08.960 --> 20:10.400
to provide an accurate enough description.

20:10.400 --> 20:12.160
Accurate. Definitely accurate.

20:12.160 --> 20:13.560
Ms. Sun, she's a teacher.

20:13.750 --> 20:15.000
A university professor.

20:15.000 --> 20:16.400
She has excellent verbal skills,

20:16.400 --> 20:18.160
-insulting people without dirty words.
-No matter how accurate she is,

20:18.160 --> 20:20.160
there would still be room
for error in my hearing and understanding.

20:20.160 --> 20:21.240
There would be no error.

20:21.240 --> 20:22.750
How could you possibly make mistakes?

20:22.750 --> 20:23.160
That's ridiculous.

20:23.160 --> 20:24.160
Don't change the subject.

20:24.160 --> 20:24.890
Listen to me.

20:26.440 --> 20:27.500
A composite sketch

20:27.510 --> 20:30.020
is drawn based on verbal descriptions.

20:30.510 --> 20:32.150
The describer's mouth and my ears

20:32.150 --> 20:33.440
aren't cameras.

20:33.720 --> 20:35.070
It's impossible to recreate

20:35.070 --> 20:36.790
the subject's appearance
with 100% accuracy.

20:36.790 --> 20:37.720
Even at its best,

20:38.240 --> 20:40.720
there's at least a 15% margin of error.

20:43.240 --> 20:44.440
Let me put it this way.

20:46.590 --> 20:49.350
If you use a composite sketch
for in-person comparison,

20:49.350 --> 20:50.550
it might be useful.

20:50.550 --> 20:52.550
Because there's such a thing
as resemblance.

20:52.550 --> 20:54.680
But if you give the sketch

20:54.680 --> 20:55.640
to a computer

20:55.640 --> 20:56.750
for facial recognition,

20:56.750 --> 20:58.110
the machine's algorithm

20:58.110 --> 21:00.370
doesn't have an option for resemblance.

21:07.310 --> 21:08.590
But I just want to know

21:08.590 --> 21:09.080
what he

21:09.680 --> 21:11.070
actually looks like.

21:13.510 --> 21:15.720
Even though you use this sketch I draw

21:15.720 --> 21:18.160
to compare with photos
in the household registration system,

21:18.160 --> 21:19.960
do you have time
to sift through tens of thousands

21:19.960 --> 21:22.550
or even hundreds of thousands of photos,
like finding a needle in a haystack?

21:22.550 --> 21:24.310
You'd be better off thinking of other ways

21:24.310 --> 21:25.510
to find other leads.

21:32.770 --> 21:35.770
[Rent across Miles, Service within Smiles]

21:33.160 --> 21:35.880
Dong A 4728K is a Land Rover.

21:36.160 --> 21:37.890
I called to confirm at the time.

21:37.960 --> 21:39.440
He rented the car from here.

21:39.440 --> 21:40.590
We've already checked the system.

21:40.590 --> 21:42.270
-There really isn't Xia Yi.
-Ma'am.

21:42.270 --> 21:44.400
You're the one who reported us, right?

21:44.680 --> 21:46.070
The police have already fined us.

21:46.070 --> 21:47.270
What more do you want?

21:47.960 --> 21:49.030
The police?

21:49.480 --> 21:50.110
I've already explained everything

21:50.110 --> 21:51.480
to Officer Li.

21:51.480 --> 21:52.400
I don't know that person

21:52.400 --> 21:53.530
called Xia Yi at all.

21:54.110 --> 21:55.840
He just gave me some extra money

21:56.160 --> 21:58.590
to use my ID card
for the car rental procedure.

21:58.590 --> 21:59.270
He returned the car on time,

21:59.270 --> 22:00.870
and there were no accidents.

22:01.200 --> 22:04.000
You shouldn't have called the police,
should you?

22:06.960 --> 22:07.590
I'm sorry.

22:15.680 --> 22:16.080
Hello?

22:18.510 --> 22:20.510
I logged into Jiale's gaming account

22:20.510 --> 22:22.160
and checked his battle records.

22:22.160 --> 22:23.500
For a while,

22:23.590 --> 22:24.000
he

22:24.000 --> 22:25.880
often played with the person
using this avatar.

22:25.880 --> 22:27.680
I suspect this person was Xia Yi.

22:27.960 --> 22:29.550
I'll send you the picture

22:29.550 --> 22:30.850
of his avatar first.

22:34.550 --> 22:35.440
Octopus.

22:54.680 --> 22:55.350
No!

23:01.720 --> 23:02.240
Zhang.

23:02.750 --> 23:04.810
Could you help me with the paperwork?

23:05.720 --> 23:06.590
Going to Gangdao again?

23:06.590 --> 23:07.160
Yes.

23:07.590 --> 23:08.790
They are all old patients I met

23:08.790 --> 23:09.880
during my internship.

23:09.880 --> 23:10.880
We've fraternized.

23:10.880 --> 23:12.930
I won't rest easy unless they're attended.

23:12.930 --> 23:14.240
Thank you for your help.

23:14.240 --> 23:14.840
Oh, right,

23:14.960 --> 23:16.070
Li Changning's condition

23:16.070 --> 23:18.000
has become much better these days.

23:18.070 --> 23:19.930
Her mother even jokes with us now.

23:20.350 --> 23:20.810
Really?

23:25.370 --> 23:30.300
[Fantian Tattoo]

23:27.510 --> 23:28.790
I have a drawing here.

23:29.440 --> 23:30.880
Those surrounding the eye

23:30.880 --> 23:32.540
should be octopus tentacles.

23:33.110 --> 23:34.960
If you recall anyone who got this tattoo,

23:34.960 --> 23:36.680
will you please let me know?

23:36.850 --> 23:42.900
[Fantian Tattoo]

23:36.960 --> 23:37.550
Chen.

23:39.240 --> 23:40.720
Did any client ask for this tattoo?

23:40.720 --> 23:41.320
This is...

23:41.750 --> 23:42.880
"the Eye of Medusa."

23:43.960 --> 23:45.020
No one asked for it.

23:45.520 --> 23:48.550
Then why were the snakes around
changed to octopus tentacles?

23:48.550 --> 23:49.280
So messed up.

23:50.510 --> 23:51.590
Thanks for your help.

23:51.590 --> 23:52.250
No problem.

23:53.890 --> 23:57.000
[Police]

23:55.110 --> 23:55.590
Wei.

23:57.200 --> 23:57.920
Where have you gone?

23:57.920 --> 23:59.450
I haven't seen you for days.

23:59.480 --> 24:00.810
I've been on field duty.

24:01.030 --> 24:02.550
A hit-and-run suspect fled back

24:02.550 --> 24:04.270
to his hometown in the Northwest.

24:04.270 --> 24:05.680
Dong and I just arrested him

24:05.680 --> 24:06.750
and are now escorting him back.

24:06.750 --> 24:07.640
A few days ago,

24:08.920 --> 24:10.400
I sent you Xia Yi's profile.

24:10.400 --> 24:11.070
Have you read it?

24:11.070 --> 24:11.480
Who?

24:11.790 --> 24:12.440
Xia Yi.

24:13.400 --> 24:14.130
Oh, that man.

24:14.440 --> 24:17.270
No one has asked
to file a report or open a case about him.

24:17.270 --> 24:18.400
What do you want me to look into?

24:18.400 --> 24:19.160
Well, look,

24:19.160 --> 24:19.960
if you're busy,

24:19.960 --> 24:20.690
my colleague

24:20.960 --> 24:22.890
and I will do the legwork, alright?

24:23.310 --> 24:24.710
Okay. I'm hanging up now.

24:27.420 --> 24:31.160
[Lihai Commercial Bank]

24:28.510 --> 24:30.510
Jian Leilei was transferred
to the VIP Service Dept.

24:30.510 --> 24:31.240
not long ago.

24:31.440 --> 24:32.070
Here are

24:32.070 --> 24:33.720
the sign-in sheets
for the client events she attended

24:33.720 --> 24:34.590
in the past few months.

24:34.590 --> 24:37.680
Most of the these activities
were wine tastings for our VIPs.

24:37.680 --> 24:39.310
I didn't find the name "Xia Yi"

24:39.310 --> 24:40.440
that you mentioned.

24:40.750 --> 24:41.470
[Sign-in Sheet]

24:41.330 --> 24:44.130
Were there surveillance cameras
in these events?

24:44.480 --> 24:45.090
No.

24:45.350 --> 24:46.720
Premium clients usually care a lot

24:46.720 --> 24:47.920
about their privacy.

24:48.050 --> 24:50.360
[Zhou Xinsheng] [Jiang Gang] [Chen Fei]

24:48.750 --> 24:50.610
Does this refer to the richest man

24:50.920 --> 24:52.550
of the city, Zhou Xinsheng?

24:53.310 --> 24:54.160
Yes, it's him.

24:57.970 --> 24:59.800
[Zhou Xinsheng]

24:59.800 --> 25:01.570
[Followed!]

25:05.090 --> 25:06.710
[Fine wine warms the heart;
Glad to be in the wine tasting]

25:06.740 --> 25:08.930
[and charity auction
held by Lihai Commercial Bank]

25:06.860 --> 25:10.720
A charity auction with wine tasting
held by Lihai Commercial Bank...

25:12.400 --> 25:14.060
Jian Leilei was indeed there.

25:16.760 --> 25:21.660
[Hello, Mr. Zhou, may I ask...]

25:21.740 --> 25:24.680
[Tattoo Entrance]

25:28.960 --> 25:29.750
Hello.

25:30.830 --> 25:32.560
Are you the owner of this place?

25:32.830 --> 25:33.200
Yes.

25:33.310 --> 25:33.790
Well,

25:34.200 --> 25:35.500
I have an inquiry.

25:35.880 --> 25:38.160
Have you done a tattoo like this?

25:38.810 --> 25:40.400
It's an eye surrounded

25:40.480 --> 25:41.480
by octopus tentacles,

25:41.480 --> 25:42.740
as this picture shows.

25:49.130 --> 25:54.660
[Tattoo Entrance]

25:53.750 --> 25:56.480
The patterns we do
are usually original designs.

25:57.270 --> 25:58.680
This one...

25:58.700 --> 26:00.700
is not that good. I've never seen it.

26:01.170 --> 26:05.580
[Tattoo services, customized designs]

26:06.000 --> 26:06.680
Donkey,

26:07.110 --> 26:07.870
this is Chubby Li.

26:07.870 --> 26:09.590
Why don't you keep this drawing?

26:09.590 --> 26:11.050
If you think of something,

26:11.480 --> 26:12.550
please call me.

26:12.550 --> 26:13.830
My number is right here.

26:13.830 --> 26:14.480
Okay.

26:47.170 --> 26:50.650
[Clinic]

26:51.670 --> 26:53.330
The paperwork for a leave of absence
has been done.

26:53.330 --> 26:54.160
Let Changning

26:54.160 --> 26:55.490
take a good rest at home.

26:55.610 --> 26:56.810
I've also picked some

26:56.830 --> 26:58.550
easy-to-read textbooks for her.

26:58.550 --> 27:00.550
She can do some reading in her spare time.

27:00.550 --> 27:02.300
Thank you so much, Ms. Yan.

27:02.350 --> 27:03.480
Please carefully observe any change

27:03.480 --> 27:05.720
in Changning's emotional state
when you're home.

27:05.720 --> 27:06.900
If she behaves

27:07.070 --> 27:08.480
differently than usual,

27:08.480 --> 27:08.920
call me

27:09.160 --> 27:10.400
or contact Dr. Luo.

27:10.400 --> 27:11.580
Thank you very much.

27:12.030 --> 27:14.170
Sorry for all the trouble
our family has caused you.

27:14.170 --> 27:15.030
Don't say that.

27:15.590 --> 27:16.680
Changning's well-being

27:16.680 --> 27:17.720
matters more than anything.

27:17.720 --> 27:18.120
Right.

27:25.880 --> 27:27.140
Have you done packing?

27:27.590 --> 27:28.610
Almost.

27:28.880 --> 27:30.000
Here are the discharge papers.

27:30.000 --> 27:30.640
Okay.

27:31.750 --> 27:33.610
Dr. Luo didn't come to work today?

27:34.440 --> 27:36.350
He's gone to Gangdao
on a business trip today.

27:36.350 --> 27:37.160
That's why he finished

27:37.160 --> 27:39.750
all the checkups
for the discharge yesterday.

27:39.750 --> 27:41.070
Do you need to see him about something?

27:41.070 --> 27:42.240
I can pass a message for you.

27:42.240 --> 27:43.160
No, nothing.

27:43.640 --> 27:45.840
I just want to thank him in person again.

27:46.660 --> 27:48.790
Well, let me know if you need anything.

27:49.070 --> 27:49.440
Thanks.

27:49.440 --> 27:50.240
Thank you.

27:50.590 --> 27:51.920
Alright. Put it in here.

27:52.780 --> 27:53.940
Thank you so much.

27:55.270 --> 27:56.310
Is everything packed?

27:56.310 --> 27:57.130
Almost.

27:57.240 --> 27:58.500
Anything left behind?

27:58.640 --> 27:59.670
Ms. Yan.

28:00.550 --> 28:01.640
Dr. Luo said

28:01.640 --> 28:02.840
you'd probably come.

28:03.400 --> 28:05.640
He asked me to give this
to you for your son—

28:05.640 --> 28:08.240
he needs someone to look after it
for a few days.

28:09.400 --> 28:09.790
Okay.

28:10.840 --> 28:12.500
Be careful with its right leg.

28:12.550 --> 28:13.810
It was injured before.

28:14.240 --> 28:15.350
Dr. Luo fixed it.

28:21.070 --> 28:21.730
Changning,

28:22.580 --> 28:24.040
get some good rest at home.

28:24.670 --> 28:25.930
Listen to your mother.

28:32.410 --> 28:33.960
[Hang Seng Bank]

28:33.980 --> 28:37.960
[Gangdao]

29:13.170 --> 29:14.010
Dr. Luo,

29:14.200 --> 29:15.240
thank you so much

29:15.560 --> 29:17.400
for taking the time to visit them.

29:17.400 --> 29:18.310
This is what I should do.

29:18.310 --> 29:19.110
Sam asked,

29:19.130 --> 29:20.480
"where is Dr. Luo?"

29:20.480 --> 29:21.680
He really misses you.

29:21.690 --> 29:22.190
Does he?

29:22.210 --> 29:22.940
Yes, he does.

29:23.270 --> 29:24.330
Sam is right there.

29:25.160 --> 29:26.420
There you are, Dr. Luo.

29:26.650 --> 29:27.510
Hello, Dr. Luo.

29:27.590 --> 29:28.070
Long time no see.

29:28.070 --> 29:28.590
Indeed.

29:29.680 --> 29:30.550
Hello!

29:31.960 --> 29:32.640
Sam.

29:33.400 --> 29:34.440
How have you been?

29:38.670 --> 29:39.590
You look good.

29:44.160 --> 29:44.790
Shan,

29:45.170 --> 29:47.030
Dr. Luo is here to visit you again.

29:51.200 --> 29:53.310
Shan's emotional state
is much more stable now.

29:53.310 --> 29:55.040
Nothing unusual has happened.

29:58.560 --> 30:00.960
I don't think I saw this behavior
last time.

30:01.030 --> 30:01.590
Really?

30:02.060 --> 30:03.310
She's been doing this a lot lately.

30:03.310 --> 30:03.870
Yes.

30:09.640 --> 30:10.200
Sam.

30:12.400 --> 30:12.960
May I?

30:13.920 --> 30:14.550
Thank you.

30:45.910 --> 30:48.040
I thought it was a sign of improvement.

32:00.580 --> 32:02.260
[Jiale told you not to worry, Dr. Luo]

32:02.280 --> 32:03.880
[He'll take good care of the hamster]

32:12.110 --> 32:12.560
Hello,

32:12.650 --> 32:13.580
is it Ms. Yan?

32:14.240 --> 32:16.300
I've seen the tattoo you asked about.

32:17.540 --> 32:18.800
A fellow tattoo artist

32:18.920 --> 32:20.310
did this pattern for a client

32:20.310 --> 32:21.570
and posted it on Weibo.

32:22.070 --> 32:22.730
Take a look.

32:25.020 --> 32:26.080
"Dream Traveler"?

32:30.290 --> 32:32.690
[Developed by Traveler Quadrant]
[Founder: Liu Ping]

32:34.960 --> 32:37.060
[Founder: Liu Ping]

32:43.920 --> 32:44.610
Mr. Yan,

32:44.680 --> 32:45.880
you said it all right.

32:46.270 --> 32:47.680
It's true that the client has

32:47.680 --> 32:49.070
s-some negative reviews now.

32:49.070 --> 32:50.160
But they're mainly focused on

32:50.160 --> 32:52.050
two parts of the action choreography.

32:52.050 --> 32:53.050
Don't worry.

32:53.350 --> 32:55.350
The design of new characters
and the scene modeling

32:55.350 --> 32:56.680
are already in progress.

32:56.680 --> 32:58.180
With sufficient funds,

32:58.360 --> 33:00.350
the quality is guaranteed to be ushered
to a new level.

33:00.350 --> 33:00.880
Mr. Liu.

33:01.790 --> 33:02.350
Mr. Yan,

33:02.440 --> 33:03.400
please give me a second chance.

33:03.400 --> 33:03.760
I...

33:04.000 --> 33:04.800
Hello? Hello?

33:06.680 --> 33:07.220
Lyu.

33:07.270 --> 33:08.440
Listen up, Lyu.

33:09.310 --> 33:10.070
What the heck is this?

33:10.070 --> 33:12.440
My money is used for quality improvement.

33:12.440 --> 33:14.680
I'm not here to be ripped off
by these ungrateful people.

33:14.680 --> 33:15.640
What garbage is this?

33:15.640 --> 33:16.480
What is this trash?

33:16.480 --> 33:17.350
Hurry, get out!

33:17.350 --> 33:18.250
Yes, yes.

33:18.440 --> 33:20.400
What's wrong with you all?

33:27.400 --> 33:27.750
What's up?

33:27.750 --> 33:28.400
I'm sorry, Mr. Liu.

33:28.400 --> 33:29.110
She insists on meeting you.

33:29.110 --> 33:30.270
What am I paying you guys for?

33:30.270 --> 33:31.240
Why haven't you driven her away?

33:31.240 --> 33:31.840
I'm sorry.

33:31.880 --> 33:33.550
Mr. Liu is having a conference!

33:33.550 --> 33:34.270
Sorry, Mr. Liu.

33:34.270 --> 33:35.640
I really need to confirm

33:35.640 --> 33:36.680
something important with you.

33:36.680 --> 33:37.830
It's related to a human life.

33:37.830 --> 33:39.820
-Can we just have a brief meeting?
-Sorry.

33:39.820 --> 33:42.880
-Are you listening, Mr. Liu?
-You really can't do this.

33:43.720 --> 33:44.450
Mr. Liu?

33:44.560 --> 33:46.070
I've never heard of this Jian Leilei

33:46.070 --> 33:48.030
you mentioned.

33:48.160 --> 33:50.270
Then why did you two go get

33:50.270 --> 33:51.200
the same tattoo?

33:52.440 --> 33:53.680
What's so odd about it?

33:53.680 --> 33:56.140
P-Patterns alike
are all over the internet.

33:56.480 --> 33:57.340
I'd like to know

33:57.440 --> 33:59.240
where you got this drawing.

33:59.550 --> 34:00.220
Also,

34:00.400 --> 34:02.230
why did you change—

34:02.680 --> 34:03.680
Medusa's snakes,

34:03.750 --> 34:04.200
into

34:04.350 --> 34:05.680
octopus tentacles too?

34:05.680 --> 34:06.400
Wait. S-Snakes?

34:06.400 --> 34:07.270
What snakes?

34:07.270 --> 34:08.230
What octopus tentacles?

34:08.230 --> 34:09.960
I don't understand a word you said.

34:09.960 --> 34:11.030
And that girl Jian Leilei,

34:11.030 --> 34:13.070
who you're talking about
—I don't know her at all.

34:13.070 --> 34:15.280
To address any doubts you may have,
call the police!

34:15.280 --> 34:16.630
Stop messing with me!

34:18.670 --> 34:19.320
Mr. Liu,

34:20.280 --> 34:22.440
before my good friend Jian Leilei
passed away,

34:22.440 --> 34:23.670
she mortgaged her property.

34:23.670 --> 34:25.870
Nobody knows where that money has gone.

34:27.920 --> 34:28.800
What I'm going to say

34:28.800 --> 34:30.060
may sound rough to you.

34:31.190 --> 34:33.250
I watched the latest financial news.

34:33.590 --> 34:34.760
Recently, your company

34:34.760 --> 34:35.320
happens to

34:35.320 --> 34:37.230
be facing financial difficulties.

34:37.230 --> 34:37.920
Shut up!

34:38.670 --> 34:39.880
What's going on?

34:40.400 --> 34:42.130
What are you doing here, Kexin?

34:43.590 --> 34:44.230
My apologies.

34:44.230 --> 34:44.860
Sorry.

34:45.590 --> 34:47.510
Why did you throw a temper tantrum again?

34:47.510 --> 34:48.070
No, I didn't.

34:48.070 --> 34:50.130
Just ignore this woman. She's crazy.

34:50.670 --> 34:52.730
How could you talk to others this way?

34:54.480 --> 34:56.639
I'm sorry. He has a bad temper.

34:56.880 --> 34:58.030
Why aren't you leaving?

34:58.030 --> 34:59.360
I'll call the security.

35:00.590 --> 35:02.120
It didn't scare you, did it?

35:04.070 --> 35:05.300
Who is she?

35:05.840 --> 35:07.110
I don't know her at all.

35:08.400 --> 35:10.860
What's the result
of the obstetric checkup?

35:10.880 --> 35:11.800
Very fine.

35:11.880 --> 35:12.340
Really?

35:28.080 --> 35:31.310
[A game developed by my husband]

35:32.740 --> 35:33.900
[Xin, be bright and happy]

35:46.360 --> 35:47.620
Why not come upstairs?

35:48.880 --> 35:50.230
You have a girlfriend now.

35:50.230 --> 35:52.000
Going to your place too often
is inappropriate.

35:52.000 --> 35:53.040
It's okay.

35:53.190 --> 35:54.120
If you want to...

35:54.900 --> 35:56.160
Well, we can talk here.

35:57.070 --> 35:57.840
What happened?

35:57.840 --> 35:59.110
I came here to tell you

35:59.670 --> 36:00.480
that I have

36:00.590 --> 36:02.840
found out
who has the same tattoo as Leilei.

36:02.840 --> 36:03.510
Let me see.

36:04.230 --> 36:06.150
He's the owner of a gaming company,

36:06.150 --> 36:06.960
named Liu Ping.

36:06.510 --> 36:08.420
[Save the picture]

36:07.680 --> 36:09.940
He's kind of a public figure.

36:10.960 --> 36:11.590
Did he tell you

36:11.590 --> 36:14.450
why the snakes were replaced
by octopus tentacles?

36:14.520 --> 36:14.970
No.

36:17.280 --> 36:19.590
You need to tell the police about it,
right?

36:19.590 --> 36:20.580
But before that,

36:20.800 --> 36:22.880
I should at least prove
he was acquainted with Leilei,

36:22.880 --> 36:24.880
or that they had some sort of connection.

36:24.880 --> 36:25.940
Well, these days,

36:26.360 --> 36:27.960
he's in urgent need of money.

36:28.360 --> 36:30.430
His financial situation is terrible.

36:30.430 --> 36:31.690
He's already married.

36:32.280 --> 36:34.480
I found his wife's Weibo account. Look.

36:34.760 --> 36:36.240
[Picking up my husband from work—
not just a daily routine]

36:36.090 --> 36:37.600
She seems rich and pretty.

36:36.260 --> 36:37.790
[But also a way to express
and convey affection]

36:37.880 --> 36:38.830
He's short of money,

36:38.830 --> 36:40.430
and his wife is very wealthy.

36:40.800 --> 36:41.110
Well,

36:41.110 --> 36:42.190
so he's targeting

36:42.190 --> 36:44.510
rich women like her for money then?

36:46.070 --> 36:47.000
I-Is it correct?

36:49.070 --> 36:49.960
Ms. Yan, look.

36:50.440 --> 36:51.840
Is Xia Yi in these photos?

37:01.660 --> 37:06.050
[Officer Li]
[Xia Yi is not in any of these photos]

37:09.280 --> 37:10.360
My work-out is done.

37:10.360 --> 37:11.440
I'll be home soon.

37:13.280 --> 37:13.840
Okay.

37:14.550 --> 37:15.110
Hello.

37:16.960 --> 37:18.820
You must be Mr. Liu's wife, right?

37:21.400 --> 37:22.480
Are you that lady I met

37:22.480 --> 37:24.190
in my husband's office that day?

37:24.190 --> 37:25.190
Yes, I am.

37:25.960 --> 37:27.360
Can I have a word with you?

37:27.960 --> 37:30.110
How do you know my husband has a tattoo?

37:30.590 --> 37:32.030
What's your relationship with him?

37:32.030 --> 37:33.690
No, please don't get me wrong.

37:35.190 --> 37:36.320
I'm a college teacher.

37:36.320 --> 37:37.320
My surname is Yan.

37:37.760 --> 37:38.840
My good friend

37:39.480 --> 37:41.320
had the same tattoo

37:42.280 --> 37:43.460
as your husband.

37:44.030 --> 37:46.090
She committed suicide some time ago.

37:46.360 --> 37:48.690
Before that,
she had taken out a huge loan.

37:51.150 --> 37:52.810
Why would she commit suicide?

37:53.840 --> 37:54.970
What a poor thing.

37:55.670 --> 37:56.990
Do you know

37:57.070 --> 37:58.670
what that tattoo stands for?

38:00.260 --> 38:02.160
That's all in the past.

38:03.070 --> 38:04.730
Liu Ping and I are married now.

38:05.280 --> 38:07.440
Everything in the past is behind us.

38:10.830 --> 38:12.320
I read your Weibo posts.

38:12.710 --> 38:15.180
You seem to be from a wealthy family.

38:15.360 --> 38:16.620
What are you implying?

38:18.030 --> 38:18.880
Has Liu Ping

38:19.960 --> 38:21.770
ever asked you for money?

38:22.280 --> 38:23.230
Ms. Yan,

38:23.400 --> 38:25.130
you're getting way out of line.

38:25.670 --> 38:26.320
I...

38:26.880 --> 38:29.070
I'm sorry
for what happened to your friend.

38:29.070 --> 38:29.590
But...

38:29.960 --> 38:31.000
you can't just assume

38:31.000 --> 38:32.630
everyone is bad based on that, right?

38:32.630 --> 38:34.670
There's nothing else I can say to you.

38:34.670 --> 38:35.710
You'd better stop

38:35.710 --> 38:37.310
harassing me and my husband.

38:37.840 --> 38:38.510
I'm sorry,

38:38.510 --> 38:39.000
Ms. Yu.

38:39.070 --> 38:41.030
If I said anything offensive,

38:41.030 --> 38:41.760
I apologize.

38:42.670 --> 38:44.850
I took offense to every word you said.

38:45.000 --> 38:46.400
If you harass me again...

38:47.400 --> 38:48.480
I'll call for help!

38:54.480 --> 38:54.960
Yes.

38:55.920 --> 38:57.980
Ms. Zhang, you're absolutely right.

38:58.800 --> 38:59.670
Only the lovestruck

38:59.670 --> 39:01.480
would be scammed.

39:01.590 --> 39:03.790
I don't think any fraud could trick you.

39:04.000 --> 39:04.920
No kidding.

39:04.920 --> 39:05.920
Lovestruck, huh?

39:05.920 --> 39:06.360
I bet

39:06.360 --> 39:09.760
you'd slap the conman so hard
that he'll collapse, Ms. Zhang.

39:10.760 --> 39:11.310
Alright.

39:12.550 --> 39:14.510
If someone reports a similar case,

39:14.510 --> 39:15.670
just let me know.

39:16.630 --> 39:17.440
Okay.

39:18.320 --> 39:18.850
Missile,

39:19.150 --> 39:20.150
this is Chubby Li.

39:20.840 --> 39:21.760
Recently, has any...

39:21.760 --> 39:22.670
Calm down!

39:22.670 --> 39:23.320
What's going on?

39:23.320 --> 39:24.480
Why is there so much noise?

39:24.480 --> 39:25.340
Think about it.

39:25.400 --> 39:27.110
You have your husband and children!

39:27.110 --> 39:29.010
The man you dated online

39:29.320 --> 39:30.780
was just after your money!

39:31.190 --> 39:32.470
Don't jump!

39:32.590 --> 39:33.740
Calm down!

39:38.670 --> 39:39.630
What do you need me for?

39:39.630 --> 39:41.130
Master, Master!

39:42.800 --> 39:43.060
Hey.

39:43.630 --> 39:44.760
Why the rush?

39:45.880 --> 39:46.670
Recently,

39:46.760 --> 39:48.360
I've asked some schoolmates

39:48.510 --> 39:49.640
and acquaintances.

39:50.030 --> 39:51.190
They told me about a few cases

39:51.190 --> 39:53.320
where romantic relationships
ended as money scams,

39:53.320 --> 39:55.670
strikingly resembling
what happened to Jian Leilei.

39:55.670 --> 39:58.000
I think there's a criminal gang involved.

39:58.110 --> 39:59.710
We should open a case on it
and start an investigation.

39:59.710 --> 40:01.760
See, Missile here came...

40:01.760 --> 40:02.220
I mean,

40:02.960 --> 40:03.630
Officer Wang Ziwen here

40:03.630 --> 40:04.550
came across a similar case.

40:04.550 --> 40:05.630
Which pricinct are you from?

40:05.630 --> 40:06.290
Chief Hu,

40:06.320 --> 40:07.710
I went to college with Li.

40:07.710 --> 40:10.230
I'm now a community officer
at Shangguan Police Station.

40:10.230 --> 40:11.800
After hearing Li's statement,

40:11.800 --> 40:13.200
I reported it to my chief.

40:13.320 --> 40:16.280
He agreed to let me come
and brief you about a similar case.

40:16.280 --> 40:17.740
Why aren't you in uniform?

40:17.920 --> 40:18.920
I'm off duty today.

40:18.920 --> 40:20.800
But Chubby Li insisted
that I come meet you.

40:20.800 --> 40:21.920
Get to the point.

40:22.110 --> 40:24.060
We responded to a call the night before.

40:24.060 --> 40:25.920
A woman attempted to jump off a building.

40:25.920 --> 40:26.820
Later on...

40:27.070 --> 40:28.140
after we rescued her,

40:28.140 --> 40:30.140
she told us that she met a man online.

40:30.510 --> 40:31.070
Then,

40:31.150 --> 40:32.560
they dated for a while.

40:32.670 --> 40:34.780
That man talked her into an investment.

40:34.780 --> 40:36.490
Just like that,
she was swindled out of her money.

40:36.490 --> 40:37.690
She and her husband

40:37.720 --> 40:38.510
had saved

40:38.510 --> 40:40.040
that money up to buy a house.

40:40.280 --> 40:41.880
Her husband then beat her up.

40:42.110 --> 40:43.320
She got so upset that she...

40:43.320 --> 40:44.680
Stop rambling on.

40:44.920 --> 40:47.070
First,
the victims were defrauded differently.

40:47.070 --> 40:47.760
One was scammed online,

40:47.760 --> 40:49.000
and the other in real life.

40:49.000 --> 40:49.480
Second,

40:50.110 --> 40:51.630
the incidents ended differently.

40:51.630 --> 40:52.510
Only the man in your case—not ours

40:52.510 --> 40:54.070
—is proven to have swindled money.

40:54.070 --> 40:54.870
Let me ask you.

40:55.000 --> 40:56.760
How can you prove
they're partners in crime?

40:56.760 --> 40:58.290
Who should we open a case on?

41:01.550 --> 41:02.190
Y-You...

41:02.190 --> 41:03.360
Why are you nodding along?

41:03.360 --> 41:04.360
Go on with the briefing.

41:04.360 --> 41:05.800
You haven't got to the point yet.

41:05.800 --> 41:07.000
Y-You take over then.

41:07.550 --> 41:08.320
That woman—

41:08.470 --> 41:09.850
I mean the one they saved

41:10.320 --> 41:11.550
—said that conman online

41:11.550 --> 41:12.630
was not only nice,

41:12.800 --> 41:14.200
but also compassionate.

41:14.400 --> 41:15.460
Most importantly,

41:16.280 --> 41:18.480
he is also a volunteer
on a maritime rescue team.

41:18.480 --> 41:18.840
Right?

41:18.840 --> 41:19.550
Yes, right.

41:19.630 --> 41:20.690
I forgot that part.

41:20.880 --> 41:22.230
Speaking of which, I remember

41:22.230 --> 41:24.230
there's one thing
I haven't told Chubby Li.

41:24.230 --> 41:26.800
That is, this person has
extensive knowledge about ocean.

41:26.800 --> 41:30.070
He once identified
a kind of toxic crab at a seafood stall.

41:30.590 --> 41:31.520
It was called...

41:31.670 --> 41:32.630
called...

41:32.630 --> 41:33.320
the...

41:33.400 --> 41:34.320
The devil crab.

41:35.150 --> 41:36.080
How did you know?

41:39.400 --> 41:40.890
Her fiancé is...

41:41.110 --> 41:42.110
A man named Xia Yi.

41:43.030 --> 41:43.590
He is

41:43.670 --> 41:45.480
a volunteer on a maritime rescue team.

41:45.480 --> 41:46.360
When we first met,

41:46.360 --> 41:47.760
he took me to a fish market.

41:47.760 --> 41:50.440
We saw a type of crab there.

41:50.440 --> 41:51.760
It looked like a flower crab,

41:51.760 --> 41:52.710
but it was actually highly poisonous.

41:52.710 --> 41:53.840
Eating it would land you
in intensive care.

41:53.840 --> 41:56.400
That was called "the devil crab."

41:57.430 --> 42:01.840
[The Dark Romance]

42:11.510 --> 42:13.470
Too much clutter at home?

42:13.710 --> 42:16.230
Wondering where to place your belongings
when you move or renovate your house?

42:16.230 --> 42:18.260
Bring your big and small items to us.

42:18.550 --> 42:20.890
U Place Mini Storage is at your service.

42:21.280 --> 42:22.820
Plenty of room is provided.

42:23.280 --> 42:24.950
Security is guaranteed.

42:25.150 --> 42:26.410
Privacy is protected.

42:27.320 --> 42:28.630
U Place Mini Storage,

42:28.920 --> 42:30.880
your personal safe.
